                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15499733" author="michael-o" created="Sat, 17 Sep 2016 21:34:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Find &lt;tt&gt;configure.out&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;config.log&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;config.status&lt;/tt&gt; in this attachment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15501163" author="brane" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2016 15:31:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like the reason is that autoconf 2.60 introduced &lt;tt&gt;datarootdir&lt;/tt&gt; and the default value for &lt;tt&gt;datadir&lt;/tt&gt; is no longer &lt;tt&gt;&quot;${prefix}/share&quot;&lt;/tt&gt; but &lt;tt&gt;&quot;${datarootdir}&quot;&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15501189" author="brane" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2016 15:48:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in r1761334 and proposed for backport to 1.8.x and 1.9.x.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15501210" author="michael-o" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2016 16:01:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Awesome, do you want me to test that?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15501294" author="brane" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2016 17:01:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Would be great if you can take time to test it, yes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15501539" author="michael-o" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2016 19:47:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just tested the fix. All is well now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15705813" author="kotkov" created="Tue, 29 Nov 2016 16:43:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix for this issue was included in Subversion 1.9.5 and 1.8.17.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
